  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q103",
  "body": "What do we pray for in the third petition?\n\nIn the third petition, which is, 'Thy will be done in earth, as it is in heaven,' we pray, That God, by his grace, would make us able and willing to know, obey, and submit to his will in all things, as the angels do in heaven.",
